  "original_title": "Elvis, Michael, Tina \u2026all in one!",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Elvis, Michael, Tina \u2026all in one!",
      "author": "Sahan Weerasooriya",
      "body_lines": [
        "I guess many of you would find it hard to believe that one person can incorporate\u2026or, let\u2019s say, impersonate three different acts at any given time!",
        "However, those who have heard of Kirthie Abeywickreme will acknowledge the fact that Kirthie is the only guy who can do it, and do it exceedingly well.",
        "Some say that Kirthie is a born entertainer, and I would add, a comedian, as well, because his impersonation of Elvis Presley, Michael Jackson, and Tina Turner also generates a lot of fun, and laughter!",
        "I\u2019ve known Kirthie for quite a while now, when he was very active in the local showbiz scene; he is now based in Germany and operates as a professional musician/entertainer.",
        "The last time I saw him do his three-in-one act was at the Monarch Imperial, in Thalawathugoda, at a sing-along event. He turned up, with a friend, and went into action, backed by Sohan & The X-Periments.",
        "What makes Kirthie standout is the outfit he wears for each act; the Elvis look, Michael Jackson\u2026and the moonwalk brought in, as well, and then a sexy looking short outfit to highlight Tina Turner.",
        "In Germany, he has his Action Show Band, called Kit \u2018N\u2019 Sunrise.",
        "The band comprises Anura Herat \u2013 ex-Moonstones (bass guitar), Kirthie Abeywickreme \u2013 ex-Des and The Clan (lead guitar), Susantha Perera \u2013 ex-Desmond and The Clan (keyboards and sax) and Musha Yehiya \u2013 ex-Steelers (drums).",
        "Says Kirthie: \u2018We now have work coming our way and we have started to perform at some of the same old night clubs where we used to play, in Germany, before the Covid issue cropped up.",
        "\u201cWe were left without work for almost two years, but the German political system helped those self-employed, and musicians, in a big way.\u201d",
        "Referring to his talent as an impersonator, he says: \u201cThank God I still can move my froggy legs to do the funny side of stars, imitating Jacko, Tina and Elvis.",
        "\u201cI\u2019m looking forward to going on until I reach the point where I cannot stand firmly on stage, anymore.\u201d",
        "Being an ex-member of the late Desmond de Silva\u2019s band, The Clan, Kirthie had this to say:",
        "\u2018My hero, Desmond de Silva Silva, celebrated his 78th birthday, in heaven, on 13th July 2022.",
        "\u201cMissing him are millions of his friends and fans, all over the world, but, most of all, his loving wife Phyllis and family.",
        "Kit \u2018N\u2019 Sunrise, from left: Anura Herat, Kirthie Abeywickreme, Susantha Perera, and Musha Yehiya",
        "Leave a Reply Cancel replyYour email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *Comment Name *",
        "Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment."
      ],
